sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant C as SearchController
    participant S as SearchService
    participant R as Redis (LRU Cache)
    participant DB as Postgres

    U->>C: GET /v1/search-flights?source=...&dest=...&date=...
    C->>S: searchFlights(request)
    
    Note over S,R: 1. Check Cache
    S->>R: GET search:{source}:{dest}:{date}
    
    alt Cache HIT
        R-->>S: JSON Result
        Note over S,R: Update MRU (Most Recently Used)
        S->>R: LREM (Remove key from LRU list)
        S->>R: LPUSH (Add key to front of LRU list)
        S-->>C: Return parsed JSON
        C-->>U: 200 OK (Schedules)
    else Cache MISS
        Note over S,DB: 2. Query Database
        S->>DB: SELECT schedules JOIN flights (Range Query)
        DB-->>S: Query Results
        
        alt Results Not Empty
            Note over S,R: 3. Store Cache & Track LRU
            S->>R: SET search:{source}:{dest}:{date} (JSON)
            S->>R: LREM (Remove old key from LRU list)
            S->>R: LPUSH (Add key to front of LRU list)
            
            Note over S,R: 4. Enforce Cache Limit
            S->>R: LLEN search:lru_tracker
            alt Size > Limit (e.g., 3)
                S->>R: RPOP (Get oldest key from back)
                S->>R: DEL (Delete oldest cached result)
            end
        else Results Empty
            Note over S: Skip cache update (Prevent Penetration)
        end
        
        S-->>C: Return Results
        C-->>U: 200 OK (Schedules)
    end
